## Problem Statement

**Current Behavior:**
- Auto-save code exists in `src/services/autoSave.ts` with all functionality implemented
- No user-facing UI to enable/configure auto-save
- No onboarding to guide users to cloud-syncing folders
- Users don't know how to backup or sync across devices

**Desired Behavior:**
- After creating first content (note/task/event), user sees backup onboarding modal
- Modal provides platform-specific instructions for 5 cloud providers
- User picks backup folder, auto-save happens invisibly
- Settings page shows backup status, allows configuration
- Comprehensive documentation for all cloud providers (Windows + macOS)

**User Impact:**
- ALL users need backups (prevents data loss)
- Users wanting cross-device sync need guidance on cloud folders
- Without this, users lose data or can't sync across devices

