## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Severity | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|------------|
| FSA API browser support limited (Firefox) | Medium | High (15% of users) | Provide clear fallback to manual export, explain browser limitation |
| Users don't understand cloud sync concept | Medium | Medium | Comprehensive documentation, clear instructions, screenshots |
| Folder picker permission denied | Low | Low | Clear error messaging, explain why permission needed, retry option |
| Cloud folder deleted/moved | Low | Medium | Detect on next save, prompt to re-select folder |
| Documentation becomes outdated (cloud UI changes) | Medium | High (over time) | Regular audits, community contributions, version date on docs |

